      "role": "user",
      "content": "thx. so when u say a \"modern\" civilization, u mean like the ones we see in the west today? i'm trying to figure out if there's a specific way these structures develop over time, or if it's more like a natural progression from those older ways to the way we live now.",
      "source": "evaluator"
